    "14468830": {
      "title": "Conditions for separability in generalized Laplacian matrices and diagonally dominant matrices as density matrices",
      "abstract": "Abstract Recently, Laplacian matrices of graphs are studied as density matrices in quantum mechanics. We continue this study and give conditions for separability of generalized Laplacian matrices of weighted graphs with unit trace. In particular, we show that the Peres\u2013Horodecki positive partial transpose condition is necessary and sufficient for separability in C 2 \u2297 C q . In addition, we present sufficient conditions for separability of generalized Laplacian matrices and diagonally dominant matrices."
    }
  }
}